44
00:03:37,458 --> 00:03:38,875
Ahórratelo, Silvo.

45
00:03:40,541 --> 00:03:42,425
Vas derechito a ver al Capitán Brutus.

46
00:03:42,625 --> 00:03:43,508
En marcha.

47
00:03:43,708 --> 00:03:46,050
