165
00:10:38,958 --> 00:10:40,500
Pero ¿y si los hubiera?

166
00:10:42,083 --> 00:10:43,333
Imagináoslo.

167
00:10:44,166 --> 00:10:45,916
¿Y si existiera un sitio...

168
00:10:46,916 --> 00:10:49,000
