222
00:15:01,166 --> 00:15:02,091
¡Fern!

223
00:15:02,291 --> 00:15:03,591
¡Fern, espera!

224
00:15:03,791 --> 00:15:05,091
Más despacio.

225
00:15:05,291 --> 00:15:07,333
